{
  "id": "adv_card_szk_04_03",
  "title": "兵藤雫 3話 世界で一番クールなアイドル",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_3d_office-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――翌日",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――Next day",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.1,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_door-open-01.m4a",
          "delay": 1333.3333332999998,
          "startTime": 1.4333333333
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 1333.3333332999998,
          "startTime": 1.4333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_03-szk001.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん……\nおはようございます……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san…\nGood morning…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 3.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "おはよう、雫\nやけに眠そうだが、夜更かしでもしたのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Good morning‚ Shizuku.\nYou look unusually sleepy‚ did you stay up late?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 7.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_03-szk002.m4a",
      "text": "昨日は徹夜だった\nサニピの昔のライブ映像を、観返してた……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I pulled an all-nighter yesterday.\nI was rewatching old live footage of Sunny Peace…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_03-szk003.m4a",
      "text": "今まで、沢山のアイドルを分析したけど……\n自分の分析をするのは変な感じ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I've analyzed numerous idols before…\nBut analyzing myself feels strange…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 22.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "昔の映像を観てどうだった？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "How was watching the old footage?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 26.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_03-szk004.m4a",
      "text": "苦行だった……昔の私は、歌もダンスも下手で……\n恥ずかしくて画面を直視出来ない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It was agonizing… In the past‚ I was bad at singing and dancing…\nIt's so embarrassing that I can't even look at the screen.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 36,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_03-szk005.m4a",
      "text": "一人で床を転がって……ずっと悶絶してた……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I was rolling on the floor alone… in complete agony…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 40.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "そ、そうか……恥ずかしさに耐えてよく頑張ったな\nそれで、雫らしいかっこ良さは見つかったか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see… You endured through the embarrassment admirably.\nSo‚ did you find your own kind of coolness?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 49.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_03-szk006.m4a",
      "text": "自分ではよく分からない、けど……\n映像を見て、思い出した……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm not quite sure myself‚ but…\nWhile watching the footage‚ I remembered…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 57.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_03-szk007.m4a",
      "text": "昔、一部のファンから言われたことがあった\nクールでミステリアスなところがかっこいいって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Back then‚ a few fans told me…\nThey found the coolness in being reserved and mysterious…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 64.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_03-szk008.m4a",
      "text": "私は話すのも笑顔も苦手で……\nだから、いつも無口で……笑えなくて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I've always struggled with talking and smiling…\nSo I was always quiet… and unable to smile…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 72.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_03-szk009.m4a",
      "text": "それが逆にクールだって、思われたのかも",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Maybe that's what made them think it's cool.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 78,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "自分でも意識せずに\nかっこ良く振る舞っていたってことか……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Unknowingly‚\nyou were acting cool‚ huh…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 83.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_03-szk010.m4a",
      "text": "でも、そう思われたのは一時期だけ\nすぐに言われなくなった……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But‚ being seen that way only lasted for a while…\nI stopped hearing those comments soon after…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 91.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_03-szk011.m4a",
      "text": "ほんのちょっと話すのに慣れて、笑顔も増えてきて……\n最初の頃と、印象が変わったんだと思う",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Just as I was getting used to speaking a bit more and smiling…\nI think my impression changed from the beginning.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 98.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "だったら、昔と同じ様にすれば\nまたかっこいいと思ってもらえるんじゃないか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Then‚ if you acted like you used to back then‚\nDo you think people might see you as cool again?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 104.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_03-szk012.m4a",
      "text": "それも難しい。昔はトークも笑顔も苦手だったから\nそうするしかなかった……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's also difficult. I used to struggle with talking and smiling…\nIt was the only way back then…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 112.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_03-szk013.m4a",
      "text": "でも今は違う……成長して、いろんなことが\n出来るようになった。今の私は、あの頃とは違う私……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But now it's different… I've grown‚ and I've become capable of various things…\nThe me now is different from the me back then…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 120.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_03-szk014.m4a",
      "text": "技術とか経験とか……全部忘れて……\n何もなかった頃に戻るなんて、無理……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Skills‚ experiences…It's impossible\nto forget them all…to go back to how things were…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 130.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "こう考えてみたらどうだ？　昔に戻るんじゃなくて\n今の雫で昔のやり方をやってみるんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "How about this perspective? Instead of going back to the past‚\nTry applying your current self to your past methods.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 139.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "成長した今なら、同じことをしても\n前よりもっといい結果が出せると思わないか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "With the growth you've achieved now‚ even if you do the same thing‚\nDon't you think you could achieve even better results?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 145.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_03-szk015.m4a",
      "text": "過去に戻るんじゃなく……\n今の自分のまま……昔やった経験を生かす……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Not going back to the past…\nRemaining as my current self… utilizing the experiences from the past…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 150.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_03-szk016.m4a",
      "text": "それは思いつかなかった……\nうん、やってみる……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I hadn't thought of that…\nYeah‚ I'll give it a try…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 158.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_03-szk017.m4a",
      "text": "昔の私も、成長した私もぜんぶ使って……\nかっこいい私に挑戦してみる……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Both the me from the past and the grown-up me…\nI'll use everything… and challenge myself to be cooler…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 165.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――広告の撮影当日",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――The day of advertisement shooting",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 169.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 171.7
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 171.9333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_03-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "もうすぐ撮影開始だ。準備はいいか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The shoot is about to start. Are you ready?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 172.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 176.2333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_03-szk018.m4a",
      "text": "ばっちり……！\n今日の撮影、しっかり見ていてほしい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Absolutely ready…!\nI want you to watch the shoot today attentively.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 177.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_04_03-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "自分らしいかっこ良さをイメージ出来たみたいだな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It seems like you've managed to imagine your unique coolness.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 181.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 184.6666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
